Package org.da.expressionj.model

Contains fundamental classes used for expressions.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
AryExpression Represent an expression with two predicates, as for example AND.
Equation An Equation interface.
Expression Repredent any expression that can be evaluated.
ExpressionType Hold the types used in Expressions.
MultipleAryExpression An expressoin with an indeterminate number of predicates.
UnaryExpression Represent an expression with one predicate, as for example NOT.
Value A value element interface, which can be a Constant or a Variable.
ValueWrapper This class cache a value.
 

Class Summary

AbstractValue An abstract value, used for Constants and variables.
